title: Frontline Assembly live At DNA Lounge, San Francisco 2006-06-06
description:
A recording of a Live webcast from June 6th, 2006 at the DNA Lounge in San Francisco. Footage is only of Front Line Assembly&#039;s performance.  Quality is about that of a 200kbps webcast, audio is tolerable, even great at some times.
